C.S.B., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPT. OF CHILDREN & FAMILIES, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4469 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 02, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Because C.S.B. has failed to serve an initial brief as provided by this court's order of February 1, 2019, this appeal is dismissed for failure to prosecute.

VILLANTI, SALARIO, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
